<custom_item>
  type           : CONFIGURATION_INFO
  description    : "2.6.1 Ensure 'Allow user to move messages from this account' is set to 'Disabled'"
  info           : "This recommendation pertains to whether a message can be moved from an institutionally configured mail account to an end-user configured mail account. It also limits forwarding or replying from a different account than that from which the message originated.
